overview: When 2nd-year nursing student Bianca  found herself struggling to adapt to online classes, she never imagined that her digital lessons would suddenly become a reality. But one fateful evening, Bianca’s world was turned upside down when she found herself right between her neighbor’s legs. Literally.  As the night wears on, Mia finds herself questioning her own abilities and the very nature of her chosen profession. But in the end, with sterile gloves on and a sprinkle of courage, it is her determination and compassion that see her through, as she learns to trust in herself and the skills she has acquired through her online nursing school.  Through this life-changing experience, Mia emerges not only as a capable nurse but also as a confident and empowered young woman, ready to take on whatever challenges come her way. Or did she?
title: Kinatao
